Name: Cross Numbers
About the game: Cross Numbers is crossword style, math based puzzle game. Numbers and operands are generated and hidden at random, and you have to complete the equations using the available tiles. RANDOMLY GENERATED Puzzles are generated at random, meaning every game is unique. SHARE WITH FRIENDS Want to solve puzzles with your friends? Share your favourite seeds with your friends to see if they can complete it faster than you. CUSTOMISABLE THEMES Don't like how the game looks? Use one of the included presets or change the theme to your exact liking.
